
--- Incident Response Frameworks ---

• NIST Incident Response Plan
• SANS Incident Response Plan


NIST Incident Response Plan

Phases:
• Preparation
• Detection & Analysis
• Containment, Eradication & Recovery
• Post-Incident Activity


SANS Incident Response Plan

Phases:
• Preparation
• Identification
• Containment
• Eradication
• Recovery
• Lessons Learned


